{"tid":1959384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺依家啲阿叔好中意偷窺","createTime":"2020-04-05T11:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T15:50:04.000Z","uid":206664,"like":21,"dislike":133,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"709e257d9e69393b22738ad87a6c95e12ff1651c","tid":1959384,"uid":206664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:02:28.000Z","msg":"以前試過同ex經過公園或者啲冇乜人嘅地方<br />\n都會攬下錫兩啖，點知有知錫錫下見到有個阿叔<br />\n定唔知阿伯喺度偷睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(嗰陣16歲)<br />\n嚇到我哋即刻走 心諗係咪痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家20歲，琴日同男朋友攬緊果陣又發現有個阿叔喺度偷睇cls<br />\n嚇到我匿埋一邊，點知個阿叔繼續偷偷地望<br />\n仲要唔小心突咗頂帽出嚟俾我男朋友發現咗<br />\n然後即刻走，嗰下真係乜mood都冇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底依家啲阿叔係有幾中意偷睇啲情侶<br />\n成件事真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a80e6ec3986d759966a6f1e65ea56a148f8d25","tid":1959384,"uid":52276,"like":373,"dislike":1,"score":372,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"咁兩個男仔係到錫，啲阿伯係好奇啲會望兩眼嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2ee2da2080c955958dc8bc82eab8398af51f86","tid":1959384,"uid":130177,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"唔係望情侶 主要係望條女"},{"pid":"8c1e815bc0803f616a290b64a9628f0b00dc81b7","tid":1959384,"uid":142676,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"唔想俾人睇到就去酒店啦<br />\n係公眾場所預咗人地見到"},{"pid":"9ffb85b25f14e6c1f80050fcb9501d2f6ba8969a","tid":1959384,"uid":35456,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:07:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31c2f40a5ef28ce6e5b5503f8e159665a81da540","tid":1959384,"uid":206664,"like":5,"dislike":39,"score":-34,"quote":{"pid":"8c1e815bc0803f616a290b64a9628f0b00dc81b7"